SUMMARY:Aniketh Mikkilineni [@axm]
DESCRIPTION:<2026-04-29 Wed 13:00-14:30>\n• ☐ HB: purchase items\n  1. PFTE
  (or nylon?) tubing\, 40ft or 12m min\n  2. Adaptors\, 2x min\n  3. Connec
 tors\, 2x min\n  4. Needle valve\n• ☑ HB: contact Glenda about mixing gase
 s and running tubing.\n• ☑ HB: measure distance to determine length of 1/4
  in PFTE tubing.\n  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
 ━━━━━\n   Distance\, ft  Description\n  ──────────────────────────────────
 ─────────────────────────\n              2  Valve to counter edge\n       
        6  From valve going up to ceiling support\n             18  Across 
 ceiling support\n              6  From ceiling support down to counter hei
 ght\n              8  From support across to UV/vis spec\n  ──────────────
 ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n             40  Total\n  ━
 ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
